        "to version 2.7, upgrade to 2.8.1 or newer or pass "
        "-DJPEGXL_ENABLE_TCMALLOC=OFF to jpeg-xl cmake line. See the following "
        "bug for details:\n"
        "   https://github.com/gperftools/gperftools/issues/1204\n")
  endif()
